lnget-ln-lnc-revoke - Revoke an LNC session


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBlnget ln lnc revoke [session-id] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Revoke and delete an LNC session.

.PP
Use --all to revoke all saved sessions.


.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fB--all\fP[=false]
	Revoke all saved sessions

